
ctime(3)             LPC LIBRARY FUNCTIONS               ctime(3)

NAME
     ctime() - return a time string

SYNOPSIS
     string ctime( int clock );

DESCRIPTION
     Gives a nice string with current date  and  time,  with  the
     argument 'clock' that is the number of seconds since 1970.

SEE ALSO
     time(3)


